revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yarberrys}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yarberry'' is the 28001<sup>st</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 856 individuals. ''Yarberry'' is most common among White (91.59%) individuals.
